1. *Čuva* se sve dok ne dođe vreme. (It is kept until the time comes.)

2. To je nešto što se *čuva* vekovima. (It is something that is kept for centuries.)

3. Svako ima nešto što *čuva*. (Everyone has something to keep.)

4. Oni su se *čuvali* da ne bi bili otkriveni. (They were careful not to be discovered.)

5. Ima nešto što bih *čuvao* za sebe. (There is something that I would keep to myself.)